So tingy and fresh. Had never tried fresh brussel sprouts before - and now have made this recipe 2 times. Couldn't easily find bresaola, so used prosciutto instead. Used balsamic vinaigrette instead of sherry wine, and turned out great. It can stand on its own without the meat as well!

